ichSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-havacilik-ve-uzay-muhendisligi/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/aerospace-engineering-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"tr","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-havacilik-ve-uzay-muhendisligi/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<div style="height:55px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Uçaklar, roketler, uydular… Teknolojiyle gökyüzüne dokunmak, belki de uzaya bir iz bırakmak mı istiyorsunuz? Türkiye, havacılık ve uzay mühendisliği eğitimi için hızla parlayan bir yıldız. Güçlü üniversiteleri, modern laboratuvarları ve TUSAŞ gibi devlerle iş birliği yapan okullarıyla bu alanda iddialı. Peki, hangi üniversiteler öne çıkıyor? Başvuru nasıl yapılır? Mezun olunca ne olur? Üstelik uluslararası bir öğrenciyseniz, Türkiye’de sosyal yaşam nasıl? Hepsini bu rehberde derledim, hadi başlayalım!</p>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-havacilik-ve-uzay-muhendisligi-nedir">1. Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği Nedir?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği, uçak, helikopter, insansız hava araçları (İHA), roket ve uzay araçları gibi hava ve uzay sistemlerinin tasarlanmasını, üretilmesini ve test edilmesini içeren bir mühendislik dalıdır. Bu alanda çalışan mühendisler, <strong>aerodinamik, itki sistemleri, yapısal tasarım, malzeme bilimi, aviyonik sistemler ve kontrol mühendisliği</strong> gibi çeşitli konular üzerinde çalışır.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Bu disiplin, <strong>Havacılık Mühendisliği</strong> ve <strong>Uzay Mühendisliği</strong> olmak üzere iki ana kategoriye ayrılır:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Havacılık Mühendisliği:</strong> Atmosfer içinde uçan araçların (uçak, helikopter, İHA) tasarımı ve üretimiyle ilgilenir.</li>



<li><strong>Uzay Mühendisliği:</strong> Uzay araçları, roketler, uydular ve derin uzay keşif sistemleri üzerine çalışır.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Dünyanın dört bir yanındaki üniversiteler, Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği alanında kapsamlı eğitim programları sunarak, öğrencileri bu ileri teknoloji sektöründe kariyere hazırlar.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="uluslararasi-havacilik-ve-uzay-muhendisligi-egitimi">Uluslararası Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği Eğitimi</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği, dünya genelinde birçok ülkede prestijli üniversiteler tarafından sunulmaktadır. Bu bölümü seçerken dikkate almanız gereken bazı önemli kriterler şunlardır:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Programın akreditasyonu</strong> (ABET, EUR-ACE gibi)</li>



<li><strong>Endüstri iş birlikleri ve staj imkanları</strong></li>



<li><strong>Laboratuvar olanakları ve araştırma merkezleri</strong></li>



<li><strong>Uzay ajansları ve havacılık şirketleriyle ortak projeler</strong></li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Öğrenciler genellikle <strong>4 yıl süren lisans programları</strong> boyunca temel mühendislik derslerinin yanı sıra <strong>hava ve uzay sistemleri tasarımı, aerodinamik analiz, motor sistemleri, aviyonik ve kontrol sistemleri, malzeme bilimi ve uzay mekaniği</strong> gibi konular üzerine eğitim alır. Bazı üniversitelerde yüksek lisans (M.Sc.) ve doktora (Ph.D.) programları da sunulmaktadır.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-turkiyede-havacilik-ve-uzay-muhendisligi-egitimi-veren-en-iyi-5-universite">2. Türkiye’de Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği Eğitimi Veren En İyi 5 Üniversite</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği, teknolojik gelişmelerin hızla ilerlediği ve <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-savunma-sanayii-havacilik/" data-type="post" data-id="9100">savunma, ticari havacılık, uydu</a> sistemleri ve uzay araştırmaları gibi birçok alanda önemli rol oynayan bir mühendislik dalıdır. Türkiye, son yıllarda <strong>TUSAŞ (Türk Havacılık ve Uzay Sanayii), ASELSAN, ROKETSAN ve TÜBİTAK Uzay</strong> gibi kuruluşlarla havacılık ve uzay teknolojilerine büyük yatırımlar yapmaktadır. Bu gelişmeler, Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği alanında eğitim veren üniversitelerin sayısını ve kalitesini artırmıştır.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">İşte Türkiye’de <strong>Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği eğitimi veren en iyi 5 üniversite</strong> ve sundukları fırsatlar!</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-orta-dogu-teknik-universitesi-odtu">1. Orta Doğu Teknik Üniversitesi (ODTÜ)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Konum:</strong> Ankara<br><strong>Dil:</strong> İngilizce</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Orta Doğu Teknik Üniversitesi (ODTÜ), Türkiye’nin en köklü ve en prestijli teknik üniversitelerinden biridir. ODTÜ’nün <strong>Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği Bölümü</strong>, 1981 yılında kurulmuş olup, dünya standartlarında eğitim vermektedir.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="neden-odtu">Neden ODTÜ?</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Uluslararası Tanınırlık:</strong> ODTÜ, dünya sıralamalarında her zaman üst sıralarda yer alan bir üniversitedir. Mezunları, NASA, Boeing, Airbus ve SpaceX gibi şirketlerde çalışma fırsatı bulmaktadır.<br><strong>Güçlü Araştırma Merkezleri:</strong> Üniversite, <strong>ODTÜ Havacılık ve Uzay Teknolojileri Merkezi (USET)</strong> ve <strong>Roket Laboratuvarı</strong> gibi tesislere sahiptir.<br><strong>Savunma Sanayi İş Birlikleri:</strong> ASELSAN, ROKETSAN ve TUSAŞ gibi dev şirketlerle ortak projeler yürütmektedir.<br><strong>İngilizce Eğitim:</strong> ODTÜ’nün Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği bölümü tamamen İngilizce eğitim vermektedir.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-istanbul-teknik-universitesi-itu">2. İstanbul Teknik Üniversitesi (İTÜ)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Konum:</strong> İstanbul<br><strong>Dil:</strong> İngilizce</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">İstanbul Teknik Üniversitesi (İTÜ), mühendislik alanında Türkiye’nin en köklü ve en prestijli üniversitelerinden biridir. <strong><a href="https://uubf.itu.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği bölümü</a></strong>, 1983 yılında kurulmuş ve sektöre birçok başarılı mühendis kazandırmıştır.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="neden-itu">Neden İTÜ?</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Gelişmiş Laboratuvarlar:</strong> İTÜ, <strong>Uçuş Mekaniği Laboratuvarı, Rüzgar Tüneli ve İleri Malzemeler Merkezi</strong> gibi laboratuvarlara sahiptir.<br><strong>Sanayi İş Birlikleri:</strong> Airbus, Boeing, Turkish Technic, ASELSAN ve TEI (TUSAŞ Motor Sanayi) gibi şirketlerle iş birlikleri bulunmaktadır.<br><strong>İstanbul’un Avantajları:</strong> Üniversite, İstanbul’da bulunduğu için öğrenciler hem havacılık sektöründeki firmalarla yakın temas kurabilir hem de uluslararası staj imkanlarından faydalanabilir.<br><strong>Uluslararası İş Olanakları:</strong> İTÜ mezunları, NASA, Lockheed Martin ve SpaceX gibi dünyaca ünlü şirketlerde çalışma fırsatı bulmaktadır.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-turk-hava-kurumu-universitesi-thku">3. Türk Hava Kurumu Üniversitesi (THKÜ)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Konum:</strong> Ankara<br><strong>Dil:</strong> Türkçe ve İngilizce</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türk Hava Kurumu Üniversitesi (THKÜ), Türkiye’de havacılığa özel olarak eğitim veren <strong>ilk ve tek</strong> üniversitedir. Üniversite, <strong>Türk Hava Kurumu tarafından desteklenmekte</strong> olup, öğrencilere doğrudan havacılık sektörüne giriş yapma fırsatı sunmaktadır.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="neden-thku">Neden THKÜ?</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Havacılık Odaklı Eğitim:</strong> Türkiye’de sadece havacılık ve uzay alanında eğitim veren tek üniversitedir.<br><strong>Pilotaj Eğitimi Fırsatları:</strong> Havacılık mühendisliği öğrencileri, pilotluk eğitimi alma şansına da sahiptir.<br><strong>Sivil Havacılık İş Birlikleri:</strong> Pegasus, SunExpress, THY Teknik ve diğer özel havayolu şirketleri ile anlaşmaları bulunmaktadır.<br><strong>Pratik Uygulama ve Staj:</strong> Üniversitenin kendi uçak bakım hangarı ve simülasyon laboratuvarları vardır.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-gebze-teknik-universitesi-gtu">4. Gebze Teknik Üniversitesi (GTÜ)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Konum:</strong> Kocaeli<br><strong>Dil:</strong> İngilizce</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Gebze Teknik Üniversitesi (GTÜ), Türkiye’nin yükselen teknik üniversitelerinden biri olup, özellikle <strong>uzay ve savunma sanayi</strong> projelerine katkılarıyla dikkat çekmektedir.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="neden-gtu">Neden GTÜ?</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Gelişen Uzay ve Havacılık Programları:</strong> Son yıllarda uzay araştırmalarına yapılan yatırımlarla birlikte bölüm hızla gelişmektedir.<br><strong>Sanayi Bölgesine Yakınlık:</strong> Üniversite, Kocaeli’de bulunduğu için <strong>savunma sanayii şirketlerine</strong> çok yakındır.<br><strong>Ar-Ge Projeleri:</strong> TÜBİTAK Uzay, TUSAŞ ve ROKETSAN ile iş birlikleri bulunmaktadır.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-eskisehir-teknik-universitesi-estu">5. Eskişehir Teknik Üniversitesi (ESTÜ)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Konum:</strong> Eskişehir<br><strong>Dil:</strong> Türkçe ve İngilizce</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Eskişehir, Türkiye’nin <strong>havacılık merkezi</strong> olarak bilinir ve Eskişehir Teknik Üniversitesi (ESTÜ), özellikle uçak bakım, havacılık mühendisliği ve savunma sanayi projelerinde öncü üniversitelerden biridir.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="neden-estu">Neden ESTÜ?</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Havacılık Şehri Avantajı:</strong> Üniversite, <strong>TUSAŞ Motor Sanayi (TEI)</strong> ve <strong>Eskişehir Havacılık Kümelenmesi</strong> ile iç içedir.<br><strong>Özel Sektör İş Birlikleri:</strong> THY Teknik, TUSAŞ, Airbus ve Boeing ile staj ve iş fırsatları bulunmaktadır.<br><strong>Havacılık ve Uzay Test Merkezleri:</strong> Üniversitenin <strong>uçuş simülatörleri, test laboratuvarları ve havacılık Ar-Ge merkezleri</strong> mevcuttur.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="sonuc-hangi-universiteyi-secmelisiniz">Hangi Üniversiteyi Seçmelisiniz?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Eğer <strong>uluslararası geçerliliği olan bir diploma ve araştırma imkanları</strong> istiyorsanız, <strong>ODTÜ veya İTÜ</strong> sizin için doğru tercih olabilir. Eğer <strong>uygulamalı eğitim ve havayolu şirketleri ile doğrudan bağlantılar</strong> istiyorsanız, <strong>THKÜ veya ESTÜ</strong> size daha uygun olabilir. Eğer <strong>savunma sanayi ve uzay teknolojileri üzerine çalışmak</strong> istiyorsanız, <strong>GTÜ</strong> doğru bir seçenek olacaktır.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-turkiyede-havacilik-ve-uzay-muhendisligi-basvuru-sureci">3. Türkiye’de Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği Başvuru Süreci</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye’de bu bölüme başvurmak isteyen uluslararası öğrencilerin aşağıdaki adımları takip etmesi gerekir:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-universite-secimi-ve-basvuru-sartlari">1. Üniversite Seçimi ve Başvuru Şartları</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Her üniversitenin kendi <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-vakif-burslari/" data-type="post" data-id="2523">kabul kriterleri vardır</a>. Genel olarak şu belgeler istenir:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Lise diploması</li>



<li>Transkript (not dökümü)</li>



<li>YÖS veya SAT sınav puanı (bazı üniversiteler kabul etmektedir)</li>



<li>İngilizce dil yeterliliği (TOEFL veya IELTS gibi sınavlar)</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-basvuru-suresi-ve-tarihleri">2. Başvuru Süresi ve Tarihleri</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Başvurular genellikle <strong>Mayıs-Temmuz</strong> ayları arasında yapılır. Ancak, bazı üniversiteler yıl boyunca başvuru kabul edebilir.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-vize-ve-oturma-izni">3. Vize ve Oturma İzni</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye’de eğitim alabilmek için öğrenci vizesine başvurmanız gerekmektedir. Vize süreciyle ilgili detaylı bilgiye <a href="https://www.mfa.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Türkiye Cumhuriyeti Dışişleri Bakanlığı’nın resmi sitesinden</a> ulaşabilirsiniz.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-burs-ve-finansal-destek-imkanlari">4. Burs ve Finansal Destek İmkanları</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">TüTürkiye, uluslararası öğrenciler için tam ve kısmi burslar sunmaya devam ediyor. Özellikle Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği alanında eğitim almak isteyen öğrenciler için devlet bursları, üniversite bursları ve özel sektör destekli burslar büyük avantaj sağlıyor.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkiyede-bir-ogrencinin-ortalama-aylik-yasam-maliyetleri-usd-cinsinden">Türkiye&#8217;de bir öğrencinin ortalama aylık yaşam maliyetleri</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Yurt konaklama: 82 &#8211; 273 USD</li>



<li>Özel konaklama (kira): 273 &#8211; 682 USD</li>



<li>Aylık yemek masrafı: 137 &#8211; 273 USD</li>



<li>Toplu taşıma: 20 &#8211; 41 USD</li>



<li>Kişisel harcamalar: 137 USD</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Burslar, öğrencilerin eğitim, konaklama ve yaşam giderlerini karşılamasında büyük bir destek sağlıyor.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-turkiye-burslari-turkiye-scholarships">1. Türkiye Bursları (Türkiye Scholarships)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Kimler başvurabilir?</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Türkiye’de lisans, yüksek lisans ve doktora eğitimi almak isteyen uluslararası öğrenciler</li>



<li>Akademik başarısı yüksek, sosyal projelerde yer almış adaylar</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Neler sunar?</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Tam burs: Üniversite harç ücreti tamamen karşılanır.</li>



<li>Aylık harçlık:
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Lisans öğrencileri için 109 USD</li>



<li>Yüksek lisans öğrencileri için 150 USD</li>



<li>Doktora öğrencileri için 204 USD</li>
</ul>
</li>



<li>Ücretsiz konaklama: Üniversite yurtlarında barınma imkânı</li>



<li>Sağlık sigortası: Tüm eğitim süresi boyunca geçerli</li>



<li>Türkçe dil eğitimi: Türkçe bilmeyen öğrencilere 1 yıllık ücretsiz dil kursu</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Başvuru Tarihleri:</strong><br><a href="http://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr" data-type="link" data-id="www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2025 yılı başvuruları</a> 10 Ocak – 20 Şubat 2025 tarihleri arasında yapılacaktır.</p>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-universite-bazli-burslar">2. Üniversite Bazlı Burslar</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye’de birçok üniversite, başarıya dayalı burslar sunmaktadır. İşte Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği bölümü bulunan üniversitelerde 2025 burs fırsatları:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="odtu-orta-dogu-teknik-universitesi-2025-burslari">ODTÜ (Orta Doğu Teknik Üniversitesi) – 2025 Bursları</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>ODTÜ Başarı Bursu: Akademik not ortalaması yüksek öğrencilere verilir.</li>



<li>ODTÜ Destek Bursu: Maddi durumu yetersiz öğrencilere sağlanan eğitim ve yemek bursu.</li>



<li>ODTÜ Uluslararası Öğrenci Bursu: Tam veya kısmi burs desteği sunmaktadır.</li>



<li>Aylık burs miktarı: 137 USD</li>



<li></li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="itu-istanbul-teknik-universitesi-2025-burslari">İTÜ (İstanbul Teknik Üniversitesi) – 2025 Bursları</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>İTÜ Uluslararası Öğrenci Bursu: Mühendislik bölümlerinde okuyan yabancı öğrencilere eğitim bursu.</li>



<li>İTÜ Sanayi Destekli Burslar: TUSAŞ, ASELSAN, ROKETSAN gibi firmalarla ortak burs programları.</li>



<li>Aylık burs miktarı: 123 USD</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="thk-universitesi-turk-hava-kurumu-2025-burslari">THK Üniversitesi (Türk Hava Kurumu) – 2025 Bursları</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Pilotaj Eğitimi Bursları: Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği öğrencilerine özel finansal destek.</li>



<li>Tam burs veya eğitim ücretinin %50’sini karşılayan burslar sunulmaktadır.</li>
</ul>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-sanayi-destekli-burslar">3. Sanayi Destekli Burslar</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği öğrencileri için en büyük avantajlardan biri, savunma sanayi şirketlerinin sunduğu iş garantili burslardır. Bu burslara başvuran öğrenciler staj yapma ve mezuniyet sonrası işe girme fırsatına sahip olur.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="tusas-turk-havacilik-ve-uzay-sanayii-bursu">TUSAŞ (Türk Havacılık ve Uzay Sanayii) Bursu</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Aylık burs miktarı: 204 USD</li>



<li>Staj ve iş garantisi: Mezuniyet sonrası işe alımda öncelik sağlanır.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="aselsan-burs-programi">ASELSAN Burs Programı</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Aylık burs miktarı: 177 USD</li>



<li>Bitirme projelerine ASELSAN desteği</li>



<li>Mezuniyet sonrası iş fırsatı</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="roketsan-burs-programi">ROKETSAN Burs Programı</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Aylık burs miktarı: 164 USD</li>



<li>Özel Ar-Ge projelerinde çalışma fırsatı</li>



<li>Mezuniyet sonrası işe alım avantajı</li>
</ul>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-mezuniyet-sonrasi-kariyer-firsatlari">5. Mezuniyet Sonrası Kariyer Fırsatları</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği mezunları için Türkiye’de ve dünya genelinde birçok iş imkanı bulunmaktadır:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Havacılık Şirketleri</strong>: THY, Pegasus, TUSAŞ gibi firmalarda mühendis olarak çalışabilirsiniz.</li>



<li><strong>Uzay ve Savunma Sanayii</strong>: ASELSAN, ROKETSAN, HAVELSAN gibi şirketlerde uzay teknolojileri ve savunma projelerinde yer alabilirsiniz.</li>



<li><strong>Araştırma ve Akademi</strong>: Üniversitelerde akademik kariyer yapabilir veya özel araştırma merkezlerinde çalışabilirsiniz.</li>
</ul>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="sonuc-turkiyede-havacilik-ve-uzay-muhendisligi-okumak-mantikli-mi">Türkiye’de Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği Okumak Mantıklı mı?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Eğer teknolojiye ilgi duyuyorsanız ve havacılık sektöründe kariyer yapmak istiyorsanız, Türkiye’de Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği eğitimi almak harika bir seçenek! Gelişen uzay ve savunma sanayi, güçlü akademik programlar ve uluslararası iş imkanlarıyla Türkiye bu alanda büyük fırsatlar sunuyor.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Başvuru süreci ve detaylı rehber için <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">roadtostudy.com</a> adresini ziyaret edebilirsiniz!</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Sıkça Sorulan Sorular</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Türkiye&#8217;deki Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği eğitimi, özellikle İstanbul Teknik Üniversitesi (İTÜ) ve Orta Doğu Teknik Üniversitesi (ODTÜ) gibi köklü üniversitelerde alınabilir.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği hangi üniversitede okunur?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Başta ODTÜ ve İTÜ olmak üzere, Eskişehir Teknik, <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/gebze-teknik-universitesi-tanitim-rehberi/" data-type="page" data-id="511">Gebze Teknik</a> ve Türk Hava Kurumu Üniversiteleri bu alanda eğitim veren ve öne çıkan kurumlardır. Diğer birçok devlet ve vakıf üniversitesinde de mevcuttur.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Uzay mühendisi kaç TL maaş alır?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Uzay mühendislerinin maaşları deneyim ve çalıştıkları kuruluşa göre değişmekle birlikte, 2025 verilerine göre ortalama aylık maaş <strong>139.800 TL </strong>civarındadır; en yüksek maaşlar 230.500 TL&#8217;ye kadar çıkabilmektedir.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Uçak mühendisliği en iyi üniversiteler Türkiye?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Uçak Mühendisliği için Türkiye&#8217;de en iyi üniversiteler İstanbul Teknik Üniversitesi (İTÜ), Türk Hava Kurumu Üniversitesi ve Gebze Teknik Üniversitesidir. Başarı sıralamaları genellikle bu kurumları işaret eder.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Havacılık ve uzay mühendisliğinin önü açık mı?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Evet, önü açıktır. Özellikle Türkiye&#8217;de savunma sanayi, havacılık projeleri ve uzay teknolojileri alanındaki yoğun yatırımlar sayesinde hem kamu hem de özel sektörde kariyer fırsatları hızla artmaktadır.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-03-19T07:58:58Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2025-10-27T11:54:24Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/aerospace-engineering-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Türkiye’de Havacılık ve Uzay Mühendisliği: En İyi Üniversiteler","title":"aerospace-engineering-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'tr' AND "slug" = 'turkiye-havacilik-ve-uzay-muhendisligi' );
UPDATE "ec_posts" SET "source_seo" = '{"title":"Studying Pharmacy in Turkey: Universities & Requirements","description":"The courses offered in pharmacy faculties cover many areas such as pharmaceutical science, clinical practice and hospital pharmacy. Students studying pharmacy","robots":"follow, index, max-snippet:-1, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large","ogTitle":"Studying Pharmacy in Turkey: Universities & Requirements","ogDescription":"The courses offered in pharmacy faculties cover many areas such as pharmaceutical science, clinical practice and hospital pharmacy. Students studying pharmacy","ogImage":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities.webp","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","twitterTitle":"Studying Pharmacy in Turkey: Universities & Requirements","twitterDescription":"The courses offered in pharmacy faculties cover many areas such as pharmaceutical science, clinical practice and hospital pharmacy. Students studying pharmacy","canonicalPath":"/en/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities/","hreflang":[{"hreflang":"tr","href":"/turkiyede-eczacilik-okumak/"},{"hreflang":"en","href":"/en/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities/"}],"jsonLd":[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":["Organization","Person"],"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kare-Logo-e1740739634958.png","contentUrl":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kare-Logo-e1740739634958.png","caption":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","inLanguage":"en-US","width":"450","height":"445"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo"}},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","alternateName":"Road to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities.webp","width":"1168","height":"880","caption":"A group of international pharmacy students in a bright university laboratory in Turkey, wearing white lab coats and safety glasses, working with test tubes and microscopes.","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities/","name":"Studying Pharmacy in Turkey: Universities &amp; Requirements","datePublished":"2025-10-30T10:37:16+03:00","dateModified":"2025-10-30T10:39:13+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Studying Pharmacy in Turkey: Universities &amp; Requirements","keywords":"Studying Pharmacy,Studying Pharmacy in Turkey","datePublished":"2025-10-30T10:37:16+03:00","dateModified":"2025-10-30T10:39:13+03:00","articleSection":"University and Programs","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"The courses offered in pharmacy faculties cover many areas such as pharmaceutical science, clinical practice and hospital pharmacy. Students studying pharmacy","name":"Studying Pharmacy in Turkey: Universities &amp; Requirements","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacy is a magical field that brings science and human life together. Developing medicines, healing in hospitals or being the boss of your own pharmacy&#8230; Which one sounds good? Turkey is a great place for pharmacy with affordable education, modern laboratories and internationally recognized diplomas. But which universities stand out? How to apply? What are the salaries and job opportunities? I explain it all in this guide, let&#8217;s get started!</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacy Education in Turkey: Overview</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The courses offered in pharmacy faculties cover many areas such as <strong>pharmaceutical science</strong>, <strong>clinical practice</strong> and <strong>hospital pharmacy</strong>. Students studying pharmacy in Turkey can <strong>open a pharmacy</strong>, <strong>work in hospitals</strong> or <strong>work in pharmaceutical companies</strong> after graduation.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-content-of-pharmacy-education-in-turkey">The Content of Pharmacy Education in Turkey</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The pharmacy program is designed to equip students with both <strong>theoretical knowledge</strong> and <strong>practical skills</strong>. The content of the program consists of the following core areas:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th>Field</th><th>Content</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Pharmacology</td><td>Effects, side effects, and use of drugs</td></tr><tr><td>Biotechnology</td><td>Drug development and biotechnological processes</td></tr><tr><td>Clinical Pharmacy</td><td>Working with patients and medication management</td></tr><tr><td>Industrial Pharmacy</td><td>Drug production and quality control</td></tr><tr><td>Hospital and Community Pharmacy</td><td>Pharmacy management and prescription control</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to these areas, students will have learned <strong>all aspects of the pharmacy profession</strong> by the time they graduate.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="language-of-education-turkish-or-english">Language of Education: Turkish or English?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacy education in Turkey is usually offered in <strong>Turkish</strong>. However, for international students and those aiming for global careers, some universities offer <strong>English pharmacy programs</strong>. <strong>English-medium pharmacy schools</strong> offer their students the opportunity to join a wider network of businesses around the world.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Marmara University (Istanbul)</li>



<li>Yeditepe University (Istanbul)</li>



<li>Hacettepe University (Ankara) &#8211; Certain courses offered in English</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you choose an English program, you may need to prove your language proficiency with exams such as TOEFL or IELTS. <strong>TÖMER (Turkish Proficiency Exam) certificate may be required for those who want to receive education in Turkish.</strong></p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-pharmacy-education-in-turkey-is-advantageous">Why Pharmacy Education in Turkey is Advantageous?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Studying pharmacy in Turkey offers many advantages, especially for international students:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>International Accreditation:</strong> Many pharmacy faculties in Turkey provide diplomas valid in Europe and other countries.</li>



<li><strong>Favorable Costs:</strong> Compared to Europe and the US, tuition fees and living costs are lower.</li>



<li><strong>Modern Laboratories:</strong> Universities have research centers equipped with up-to-date technology.</li>



<li><strong>Double Major and Minor Opportunities:</strong> Some universities allow students to study additional fields such as <strong>biotechnology, chemistry or health management</strong>.</li>



<li><strong>Internship and Job Opportunities in Turkey:</strong> Students studying pharmacy in Turkey have the opportunity to do internships in large pharmaceutical companies and public hospitals.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The language of instruction is usually <strong>Turkish</strong>, but some universities also offer <strong>English pharmacy programs</strong>. <strong>English programs are a great advantage for students aiming for international careers.</strong></p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-best-pharmacy-faculties-for-foreign-students-in-turkey">The Best Pharmacy Faculties for Foreign Students in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">More than <strong>50 universities</strong> in Turkey offer pharmacy education. However, the faculties that stand out in terms of quality of education, language options and scholarship opportunities for foreign students are as follows:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="turkeys-top-5-best-pharmacy-faculty">Turkey&#8217;s Top 5 Best Pharmacy Faculty</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th>University</th><th>City</th><th>Language of Instruction</th><th>Key Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Hacettepe University</td><td>Ankara</td><td>Turkish</td><td>Ranked high in QS rankings, strong academic staff</td></tr><tr><td>Istanbul University</td><td>Istanbul</td><td>Turkish</td><td>One of the oldest pharmacy faculties in Turkey</td></tr><tr><td>Ege University</td><td>Izmir</td><td>Turkish</td><td>Modern laboratories, strong connections with the pharmaceutical industry</td></tr><tr><td>Marmara University</td><td>Istanbul</td><td>Turkish</td><td>Education aligned with European standards, ideal for international students</td></tr><tr><td>Yeditepe University</td><td>Istanbul</td><td>English</td><td>Scholarship opportunities, facilities of a private university</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These faculties are accredited by the Council of Deans of Faculties of Pharmacy of Turkey (EFDK) and the Council of Higher Education (YÖK).</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-hacettepe-university-faculty-of-pharmacy-ankara">1. Hacettepe University Faculty of Pharmacy (Ankara)</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Hacettepe University is one of the most prestigious pharmacy faculties in <strong>Turkey</strong> and ranks high in the <strong>QS World University Rankings</strong>. It offers both <strong>Turkish and English programs</strong> for foreign students.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="highlights">Highlights:</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>International Accreditation:</strong> A diploma recognized in Europe and worldwide</li>



<li><strong>Modern Research Laboratories:</strong> Pharmaceutical biotechnology and drug development projects</li>



<li><strong>High Employment Rate:</strong> Graduates have ample job opportunities in the pharmaceutical industry and hospitals</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Hacettepe University is especially ideal for research-oriented students. It is one of the best choices for students who want to pursue an <strong>academic career</strong> or <strong>turn to the pharmaceutical industry</strong> in Turkey.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-istanbul-university-faculty-of-pharmacy-istanbul">2. Istanbul University Faculty of Pharmacy (Istanbul)</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Istanbul University is one of the oldest and well-established pharmacy faculties in Turkey. <strong>As a state university, tuition fees are more affordable</strong> and it is known for its quality academic staff.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="highlights">Highlights:</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Hospital and Clinical Collaborations:</strong> Internship opportunities at university hospitals</li>



<li><strong>Strong Alumni Network:</strong> Alumni working in many pharmaceutical companies in Turkey and abroad</li>



<li><strong>Rooted Educational Tradition:</strong> One of the first pharmacy faculties in Turkey</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is one of the best options for foreign students who want to study in Turkish and are looking for a high quality education at a <strong>low cost</strong>.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-ege-university-faculty-of-pharmacy-izmir">3. Ege University Faculty of Pharmacy (Izmir)</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ege University in Izmir is a good option for international students interested in studying pharmacy, thanks to its <strong>modern laboratories and strong links with the pharmaceutical industry</strong>.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="highlights">Highlights:</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Practical Training:</strong> Students can do internships in laboratories and hospitals</li>



<li><strong>Collaborations with the Pharmaceutical Industry:</strong> Connections with Turkey&#8217;s leading pharmaceutical companies</li>



<li><strong>Cost of Living Advantage:</strong> Izmir is a more affordable student city than Istanbul</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is a faculty that provides education in Turkish, but you can get education with <strong>TÖMER Turkish proficiency exam</strong>.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-marmara-university-faculty-of-pharmacy-istanbul">4. Marmara University Faculty of Pharmacy (Istanbul)</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Marmara University is one of the few state universities that offers <strong>English pharmacy education</strong>. <strong>Provides education in accordance with the European Standards for Pharmacy Education (EAFP).</strong></p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="highlights">Highlights:</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>English Education:</strong> An attractive option for international students</li>



<li><strong>Entrepreneurship and Business Programs in Pharmacy:</strong> Special courses for those who want to become a self-employed pharmacist</li>



<li><strong>Clinical Practice and Internship Opportunities:</strong> Direct collaborations with hospitals and pharmaceutical companies</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to study in English and get a diploma that meets European standards, Marmara University may be a good option.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-yeditepe-university-faculty-of-pharmacy-istanbul">5. Yeditepe University Faculty of Pharmacy (Istanbul)</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Yeditepe University is one of the top private universities in Turkey and offers a <strong>completely English-language pharmacy program.</strong> Being a private university, it offers <strong>more scholarships and financial support</strong>.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="highlights">Highlights:</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>English Education:</strong> Diploma valid in Europe and the USA</li>



<li><strong>Advanced Research Facilities:</strong> Scientific studies in modern laboratories</li>



<li><strong>International Exchange Programs:</strong> Erasmus and internship opportunities abroad</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Since it is a private university, <strong>fees may be higher</strong> than state universities, but you have the chance to get scholarships depending on your academic success.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">What should you pay attention to when choosing pharmacy in Turkey?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is important for foreign students who want to study pharmacy in Turkey to pay attention to the following criteria when choosing a university:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Language of instruction:</strong> Do you want to study in English or Turkish? </li>



<li><strong>Fees and Scholarship Opportunities:</strong> There are big differences in fees between private and public universities.</li>



<li><strong>Internship and Job Opportunities:</strong> You should prefer universities that cooperate with pharmaceutical companies or hospitals.</li>



<li><strong>Research Facilities:</strong><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/scientific-research-projects-in-turkey/" data-type="link" data-id="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-bilimsel-arastirma-projeleri/">If you are interested in scientific studies</a>, you should choose faculties with strong laboratories.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-application-process-for-pharmacy-faculties-in-turkey">3. Application Process for Pharmacy Faculties in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Foreign students must fulfill certain application requirements to study pharmacy in Turkey. Here is the step-by-step application process:</p>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="📌-1-prepare-required-documents">


<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">📌 1. Prepare the Required Documents</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The main documents required in the application are:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>High school diploma (in Science or Health)</li>



<li>Transcript (Transcript)</li>



<li><strong>Exam Result Certificate:</strong> SAT, YÖS (Foreign Student Exam) or the university&#8217;s own entrance exam</li>



<li>Passport photocopy</li>



<li>Motivational letter (some universities may require it)</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="show-2nd-language-proficiency">📌 2. Demonstrate Language Proficiency</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>For English programs</strong>: TOEFL or IELTS certificate required.</li>



<li><strong>For Turkish programs</strong>: TÖMER (<a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiyede-tomer-turkce-ogretim-merkezleri/" data-type="post" data-id="8067">Turkish Proficiency Certificate</a>) may be required.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you do not have a qualification certificate, you can enroll in the <strong>preparatory program offered by the university.</strong></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3rd-apply-online">📌 3. Apply Online</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications are usually made through the official websites of universities.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="get-your-4th-acceptance-letter-and-apply-for-visa">📌 4. Receive Your Acceptance Letter and Apply for a Visa</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">After your application is accepted, you will receive a <strong>acceptance letter</strong> from the university. With this letter you can apply for a student visa in Turkey.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-pharmacy-education-fees-and-scholarships-in-turkey">4. Pharmacy Education Fees and Scholarships in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacy education in Turkey is much more affordable compared to Europe and the US. Here are the annual fees by university type:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<tr>
<th><strong>Type of University</strong></th>
<th><strong>Annual Tuition (USD)</strong></th>
</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>State Universities</strong></td>
<td>1.500 &#8211; 5,000</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Foundation (Private) Universities</strong></td>
<td>8,000 &#8211; 20,000</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-options">Scholarship Options</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are several scholarship programs for foreign students in pharmacy in Turkey. Here are some scholarship programs you can apply for:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong><a href="https://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Turkey Scholarships</a></strong> &#8211; Offers full scholarships to foreign students. It covers training, accommodation and monthly allowance.</li>



<li><strong>University Internal Scholarships</strong> &#8211; There are foundation universities that offer merit-based scholarships.</li>



<li><strong>TUBITAK Scholarships</strong> &#8211; Provides support to talented students in the fields of science and research.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications for scholarships usually open in <strong>January-March</strong>, so it&#8217;s important to apply early! </p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-free-pharmacist">1. Free Pharmacist</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacists are responsible for ensuring that patients take their medicines safely and providing health counseling. Pharmacy graduates in Turkey can work independently by opening their own pharmacies.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="requirements-to-become-a-freelance-pharmacist">Requirements to Become a Freelance Pharmacist</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Having a pharmacy degree in Turkey</li>



<li>Registering with the Turkish Pharmacists Association</li>



<li>Get the necessary permits to open a pharmacy</li>



<li>Doing deals with pharmaceutical suppliers</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The advantages of working as a self-employed pharmacist include the possibility to work independently, the opportunity to communicate directly with patients and doctors, and the chance to earn a stable income in the long term. However, issues such as the capital required to open a pharmacy and the choice of location should be well planned.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2-hospital-pharmacist">2. Hospital Pharmacist</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Hospital pharmacists work in hospitals, supporting doctors and nurses with medication management. <strong>Ensuring that patients use the right medicines in the right doses is one of the most important tasks of this profession.</strong></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="duties-of-the-hospital-pharmacist">Duties of the Hospital Pharmacist</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Giving patients information about prescription medicines</li>



<li>Counseling doctors and nurses on drug interactions</li>



<li>Managing medicine stocks within the hospital</li>



<li>Participating in clinical trials</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacists who want to work in this field can usually find jobs in public or private hospitals. For those who want to work in public hospitals, the <strong>Public Personnel Selection Exam (KPSS)</strong> is mandatory.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-specialization-in-the-pharmaceutical-industry">3. Specialization in the Pharmaceutical Industry</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey has a rapidly growing pharmaceutical industry. Graduates can pursue careers in different fields such as pharmaceutical manufacturing, quality control, clinical research and regulatory affairs.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="fields-to-work-in-the-pharmaceutical-industry">Fields to Work in the Pharmaceutical Industry</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>R&amp;D (Research and Development):</strong> Contributing to the development of new medicines</li>



<li><strong>Quality Control:</strong> Testing the safety and efficacy of manufactured medicines</li>



<li><strong>Regulation and Licensing:</strong> Ensuring that medicines go through legal processes</li>



<li><strong>Marketing and Sales:</strong> Promoting medicines to doctors and pharmacists</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, major pharmaceutical companies such as <strong>Abdi İbrahim, Deva Holding, Bilim Pharmaceuticals, Sanovel</strong> offer career opportunities for pharmacists.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-academic-career-faculty-member-and-researcher">4. Academic Career (Faculty Member and Researcher)</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacists who want to pursue an academic career can work as researchers or lecturers at universities. Academics can specialize in areas such as the discovery of new drugs, pharmacology studies and clinical research.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="steps-necessary-for-an-academic-career">Steps Necessary for an Academic Career</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Completing a bachelor&#8217;s degree in Pharmacy in Turkey</li>



<li>Applying to master&#8217;s and doctoral programs</li>



<li>Academic research and publications</li>



<li>To work as a lecturer or professor at universities</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic careers are a long-term process, but for those interested in scientific research, it can be a very satisfying path.</p>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 22px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="is-pharmacy-education-in-turkey-the-right-choice-for-you">Is Pharmacy Education in Turkey the Right Choice for You?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are looking for a quality education, affordable tuition and an international career, studying pharmacy in Turkey can be a great option.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can visit <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/">roadtostudy.com</a> to get guidance on the application process and choose the best university! </p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="which-is-the-best-pharmacy-faculty">Which is the best pharmacy faculty?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Among the best pharmacy faculties in Turkey, Yeditepe University, Istanbul University and Hacettepe University stand out. Yeditepe University stands out with a success ranking of 23,352.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="can-you-study-pharmacy-for-money">Can you study pharmacy for money?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Paid pharmacy departments can also offer quality education, but the academic staff, facilities and employment rates of graduates should be taken into account when choosing a faculty.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="are-there-any-jobs-in-pharmacy">Are there any jobs in pharmacy?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacy graduates can find jobs in hospitals, pharmaceutical companies, pharmacies and public institutions. As the sector grows, job opportunities also increase.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="best-pharmacy-faculty-in-turkey">Best pharmacy faculty in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, well-established public universities such as Hacettepe University, Istanbul University and Ege University are among the best pharmacy faculties.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="does-pharmacy-have-a-future">Does pharmacy have a future?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Pharmacy is one of the professions with a future as an important part of the health sector. With advances in pharmaceutical and health technologies, it is in constant demand.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="are-pharmaceuticals-dead">Are pharmaceuticals dead?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">A generalization that pharmacy is closed is not correct. Job opportunities continue with the right areas of specialization and up-to-date information.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-10-30T07:37:16Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2025-10-30T07:39:13Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities.webp","alt":"A group of international pharmacy students in a bright university laboratory in Turkey, wearing white lab coats and safety glasses, working with test tubes and microscopes.","title":"studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'studying-pharmacy-in-turkey-universities';
