<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Mimar Sinan, Hacettepe, Ankara, Gaziantep and Istanbul Technical University State Conservatories are among the most respected and well-established institutions.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-are-the-institutions-providing-music-education-in-turkey">What are the institutions providing music education in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">State conservatories, faculties of fine arts, faculties of education and private music academies offer music education.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">Which university to study for acting?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is one of the best choices to study acting at the conservatories of Mimar Sinan University, Beykent University, Maltepe University, Dokuz Eylül University and Istanbul Aydın University.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-11-03T07:13:33Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2025-11-03T07:20:41Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/music-and-performing-arts-education-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Music and Performing Arts Education in Turkey: Best Universities and Guide","title":"music-and-performing-arts-education-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'music-and-performing-arts-education-in-turkey' );
