<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="1-akdeniz-university-faculty-of-tourism-antalya">1. Akdeniz University &#8211; Faculty of Tourism (Antalya)</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-choose-it">Why Choose It?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Located in Antalya, Turkey&#8217;s most touristic city, <strong>Akdeniz University Faculty of Tourism</strong> stands out with its direct access to the industry. Students have the opportunity to apply their theoretical knowledge in the field by making direct contact with luxury hotels, resorts and travel agencies during the training process.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="features">Features:</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">✔ Collaborations with 5-star hotels and compulsory internship programs<br>✔ English and Turkish education options<br>✔ Practical training opportunities thanks to the university&#8217;s own practice hotel</p>


