<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-choose-it">Why Choose It?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Known for its proximity to tourist centers such as Bodrum, Marmaris and Fethiye, <strong>Muğla Sıtkı Koçman University</strong> is one of the few faculties offering special courses in marine tourism and yachting.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="features">Features:</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">✔ Marine tourism and yachting courses<br>✔ Extensive internship opportunities in hotels and resorts in the region<br>✔ Special programs on cultural heritage tourism and ecotourism</p>


