<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-izmir-katip-celebi-university-faculty-of-tourism-izmir">4. Izmir Katip Çelebi University &#8211; Faculty of Tourism (Izmir)</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-it-should-be-preferred">Why it should be preferred</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Izmir has a great potential in the tourism sector in terms of both accommodation and gastronomy. <strong>Izmir Katip Çelebi University</strong> has a strong academic staff in the field of <strong>gastronomy and culinary arts</strong> as well as hotel management education.</p>



