<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="5-cappadocia-university-tourism-management-and-guidance-nevsehir">5. Cappadocia University &#8211; Tourism Management and Guidance (Nevşehir)</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-it-should-be-preferred">Why it should be preferred</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Located in a touristic region like Cappadocia, <strong>Cappadocia University</strong> offers an ideal option for students who want to specialize in <strong>tourist guiding and boutique hotel management</strong>.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="features">Features:</h3>



