<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-how-to-apply-to-the-department-of-tourism-and-hotel-management-in-turkey">3. How to Apply to the Department of Tourism and Hotel Management in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To study this program in Turkey, you must follow these steps:</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applying to a tourism and hotel management program in Turkey is similar to the application process for other university programs, although some universities may require additional requirements or exams specific to this field. Below, we have detailed the application process for local and international students who wish to study tourism and hotel management in Turkey.</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="31-general-application-process">3.1 General Application Process</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To study tourism and hotel management in Turkey, you should follow these steps:</p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Prepare your high school diploma and transcript.</li>



<li>Check if language proficiency certificate is required.</li>



<li>Perform your registration process through the online application systems of universities.</li>



<li>Pay the required application fees and upload your documents.</li>



<li>Some universities may have interviews or additional exams, find out the details.</li>
</ol>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-2-tourism-and-hospitality-area-special-applications-var-mi">


<h3 class="wp-block-heading wp-block-paragraph">3.2 Are There Special Applications for Tourism and Hospitality?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There is no special central exam or separate application process for tourism and hotel management education in Turkey, but some universities may set additional criteria for certain fields. Here are some sections and additional requirements:</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="special-requirements-for-the-department-of-tourist-guidance">Special Requirements for the Department of Tourist Guidance</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The following requirements may sometimes be required of students applying for tourist guiding programs:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Language Proficiency:</strong> Knowledge of at least one foreign language such as English, German, French is required.</li>



<li><strong>Interview or Language Test:</strong> Some universities in Turkey may conduct interviews to test the language skills of guidance students.</li>



<li><strong>TÜRSAB Approved Internship Obligation:</strong> There may be an obligation to do an internship in certain tourism agencies before graduation.</li>
</ul>


<blockquote class="wp-block-quote">


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To become a professional tourist guide in Turkey, you can check out the certification programs determined by <strong><a href="https://www.tursab.org.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TÜRSAB (Association of Turkish Travel Agencies)</a></strong>.</p>


</blockquote>


<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="special-requirements-for-the-department-of-gastronomy-and-culinary-arts">Special Requirements for the Department of Gastronomy and Culinary Arts</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some universities may require the following conditions for students who want to study in this department:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Skill Exam:</strong> Some universities may have exams that measure basic culinary skills for the culinary department.</li>



<li><strong>Portfolio or Interview:</strong> If you have previous kitchen experience, you may be asked for a portfolio or work samples.</li>



<li><strong>Prerequisites for Practical Courses:</strong> Preliminary training such as hygiene and food safety may be mandatory.</li>
</ul>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="special-requirements-for-the-department-of-hotel-management-and-tourism-management">Special Requirements for the Department of Hotel Management and Tourism Management</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Mandatory Internship Program:</strong> Most tourism faculties require 1 to 2 semesters of mandatory internship.</li>



<li><strong>English Proficiency:</strong> Since hotel management and international tourism management departments generally teach in English, a language certificate may be mandatory.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="33-tourism-education-in-turkey-for-foreign-students-application">3.3 Tourism Education in Turkey for Foreign Students Application</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are a foreign student, you can apply through the <strong>Foreign National Student Examination (YÖS)</strong> or international exams.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="required-documents">Required Documents:</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>High school diploma (translated into Turkish and notarized)</li>



<li>Passport photocopy</li>



<li>Exam results such as YÖS, SAT, ACT (varies according to the university)</li>



<li>Language proficiency certificate (TOEFL, IELTS or TÖMER)</li>



<li>Motivational letter (compulsory in some universities)</li>



<li>Reference letters (may be required in some private universities)</li>
</ul>


<blockquote class="wp-block-quote">


<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Tip:</strong> Many universities have scholarship programs for foreign students who want to study tourism in Turkey. Check out the <strong><a href="https://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Turkey Scholarships</a></strong> program to discover scholarship opportunities to cover your education costs.</p>


</blockquote>
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-post-graduation-career-opportunities">4. Post-Graduation Career Opportunities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">After graduating from this field, you can follow these career paths:</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Tourism and hotel management education offers graduates a wide range of careers. There are many different sectors where you can work in Turkey or internationally. Whether you manage a hotel or open your own restaurant, this sector offers dynamic and lucrative career opportunities. Here are the most popular career paths you can consider after graduation:</p>


<div style="height:22px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
