<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-happens-to-those-who-study-tourism-and-hotel-management-for-2-years">What happens to those who study Tourism and Hotel Management for 2 years?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Graduates can work as management candidates or staff in hotels, agencies, tour companies, airlines and cruise companies.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-are-tourism-activities-in-turkey">What are tourism activities in Turkey?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Cultural tourism, sea tourism, health tourism, winter tourism, faith tourism and congress tourism are the main activities.</p>



