<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Department of Nutrition and Dietetics is a discipline that aims to create nutrition programs to protect human health, organize nutrition plans to combat diseases, and improve public health. Students studying in this department specialize in subjects such as nutrition sciences, food chemistry, clinical dietetics, and metabolism.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="in-which-universities-does-the-department-of-nutrition-and-dietetics-exist">In Which Universities Does the Department of Nutrition and Dietetics Exist?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many public and foundation universities in Turkey offer Nutrition and Dietetics programs. Here are some of the best universities:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>
<div><strong>University</strong></div>
</th>
