<li><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ankara-universitesi/" data-type="page" data-id="372">For More Information: <strong><strong>Ankara University</strong></strong></a></li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="3-istanbul-university-faculty-of-political-sciences">3. Istanbul University &#8211; Faculty of Political Sciences</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Istanbul University, one of the oldest universities in Turkey, has a strong infrastructure both historically and academically.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong><strong>Why to Choose?&#8221;</strong><br> Extensive academic resources, active student clubs and community research projects.</strong></li>



<li><strong><strong>Application Tips:</strong><br>Promote research-oriented work.</strong></li>



<li><strong><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/istanbul-universitesi-2/" data-type="page" data-id="412">For More Information: <strong><strong><strong><strong>Istanbul University</strong></strong></strong></strong></a></strong></li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="4-middle-east-technical-university-metu-political-science-and-public-administration">4. Middle East Technical University (METU) &#8211; Political Science and Public Administration</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">ODTÜ is known for its innovative education approach and strong academic staff. The opportunity to study in English is a great advantage for international students.</p>



