<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How much does Political Science and Public Administration earn?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The average monthly salary of a Public Relations Specialist is set at&nbsp;<strong>48,200 TL (1,205 USD)</strong>. In 2025, the lowest salary is&nbsp;<strong>40,000 TL (1,000 USD)</strong>&nbsp;and the highest is&nbsp;<strong>65,600 TL (1,640 USD)</strong>.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-20T08:09:42Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2025-08-20T08:10:45Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/turkiye-siyaset-bilimi-ve-kamu-yonetimi.webp","alt":"Political Science and Public Administration in Turkey: Which Program to Choose?","title":"turkiye-siyaset-bilimi-ve-kamu-yonetimi"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'political-science-public-administration-in-turkey' );
